 "6945365255587744"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1733851139, "id": "7000899216701014", "version": "24.12.10", "version_code": 119, "release_status": "PENDING", "status": "DRAFT", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "3388893331234972", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "6945365255587744"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "3145234072412483"}]}, "change_log": "It's the holiday season, so it's time for the return of Grokit Winter Blast! \u2744\ufe0f\n\nGo head to head with your friends in holiday themed versions of your favorite Grokit Games:\n\n\ud83c\udf32 DECORATE Christmas trees & see who can hang the most ornaments\n\ud83c\udf81 DELIVER presents into windows to keep the kids happy\n\ud83d\udca5 PASS the ornament bomb around, but don't be the one holding it when it goes BOOM\n\ud83d\udc31 RIP your presents open with your cat claws, but don't shatter the bulbs!!\n\u2603\ufe0f BLAST as many snowmen as you can by firing snowballs from your hands\n\nThis update also fixes a slew of odds and ends behind the scene to make for a smoother overall experience.\nWe've also made it easier than ever to get into multiplayer with your friends. Simply create a  multiplayer game, then use the friend invite option in the Quest universal menu to invite everyone directly. That's it! Then you're ready to Grok and roll! \n\nMany features are new and experimental, including direct game invites. Please reach out on our Discord if you run into any issues!\n\nWe appreciate any feedback, please be sure to let us know what you think. Horizon Store reviews are the best way to support Grokit and to help us make the game even better. If you haven't yet, be sure to drop a review on our store page!\n\nHappy holidays and happy grokking!", "created_date": 1732919778, "id": "6945365255587744", "version": "24.11.29", "version_code": 118, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}]}}, "viewer": {"user": null}}}